title: "Jose Carnival " and Atsab Khwaks
subtitle: Another trick from Mazab's malignant program is spreading this time warning that Carnaval de Las Palomitas or Carnival pirate can "break through" your phone.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: A Watsap video called "Carnaval de las Plomitas" or "Popcorn Carnival" hacks users' phones.
